    </node>
    <node id="Goodthink">
      <data key="d0">Goodthink</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Goodthink refers to 'orthodoxy' or the practice of thinking in an orthodox manner within the context of Newspeak.&lt;SEP&gt;Goodthink is a Newspeak term related to positive or accepted thought, reflecting Ingsoc principles.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-72158fb48dfe5cb1a9c716f76eae16d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6180f0140c592fb4bd1c07a384d5423</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1781752396</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Minipax">
      <data key="d0">Minipax</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Minipax is another Newspeak term possibly referring to a reduced form of conflict or peace within the context of Ingsoc.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d6180f0140c592fb4bd1c07a384d5423</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1781752397</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Sexcrime">
      <data key="d0">Sexcrime</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Sexcrime could be a term used in Newspeak for crimes related to sexuality, potentially reflecting Ingsoc's moral and ethical framework.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d6180f0140c592fb4bd1c07a384d5423</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1781752397</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Joycamp">
      <data key="d0">Joycamp</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Joycamp is likely a Newspeak term denoting concentration camps or work camps under Ingsoc.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d6180f0140c592fb4bd1c07a384d5423</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1781752397</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Thinkpol">
      <data key="d0">Thinkpol</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Thinkpol refers to Thought Police, an organization that enforces conformity of thought within Ingsoc.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d6180f0140c592fb4bd1c07a384d5423</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1781752397</data>
    </node>
    <node id="B Vocabulary">
      <data key="d0">B Vocabulary</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">The B vocabulary consists of words deliberately constructed for political purposes to impose a desirable mental attitude on the user.&lt;SEP&gt;The B vocabulary consists of short, easily pronounceable words designed for political and ethical judgements under Ingsoc.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-72158fb48dfe5cb1a9c716f76eae16d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6180f0140c592fb4bd1c07a384d5423</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1781752397</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Thought Police">
      <data key="d0">Thought Police</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Thought Police is another name for Thinkpol, an organization that enforces conformity of thought within Ingsoc.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d6180f0140c592fb4bd1c07a384d5423</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1781752398</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Oceania">
      <data key="d0">Oceania</data>
      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">Oceania is a fictional super-state where Newspeak is being implemented.</data>
