      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">UNGOOD expresses the opposite meaning of GOOD in Newspeak.&lt;SEP&gt;UNGOOD refers to a statement that appears self-evidently absurd but cannot be argued against due to the lack of appropriate words.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e344b38beed08083660fea5486c5abe3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-563c6c743b686961b6884d542125ac31</data>
