      <data key="d0">A Vocabulary</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">The A vocabulary consists of words for everyday life such as eating, drinking, working, and physical actions.&lt;SEP&gt;A Vocabulary refers to the more traditional English vocabulary.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-491b3d4aaf8461a08befc0aab83f4bba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc8d92b2ecc0fa26ebda9e2c6d77c94d</data>
