    <edge source="Ingsoc" target="Newspeak">
      <data key="d6">3.0</data>
      <data key="d7">Newspeak is designed to support the ideology of Ingsoc and make heretical thoughts literally unthinkable.&lt;SEP&gt;Newspeak reflects Ingsoc ideology through euphony and controlled vocabulary, aiding in thought control.&lt;SEP&gt;Words inimical to Ingsoc can only be vaguely entertained or broadly condemned using Newspeak's limited vocabulary.</data>
      <data key="d8">ideological control,ideology reflection,language design,linguistic control,opposition,restricted vocabulary</data>
      <data key="d9">chunk-6a5e67b8589ccc49c8c351f04a3fb597&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6180f0140c592fb4bd1c07a384d5423&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e344b38beed08083660fea5486c5abe3</data>
      <data key="d10">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d11">1781752424</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="Ingsoc" target="Thinkpol">
      <data key="d6">1.0</data>
      <data key="d7">The purpose of Thinkpol is to enforce conformity with Ingsoc ideology by suppressing dissenting thoughts.</data>
