    <edge source="Newspeak" target="Oldspeak">
      <data key="d6">3.0</data>
      <data key="d7">Oldspeak is being replaced by Newspeak in Oceania to limit alternative modes of thought.&lt;SEP&gt;With Oldspeak being replaced by Newspeak, many concepts from Oldspeak will become nameless and unimaginable in the future.&lt;SEP&gt;The superseding of Oldspeak by Newspeak severed the last connection with the past.</data>
      <data key="d8">historical context,historical link,language evolution,language replacement,replacement,replacement attempt</data>
      <data key="d9">chunk-6a5e67b8589ccc49c8c351f04a3fb597&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-877c954ec93bb835f0176da84c3b5889&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e344b38beed08083660fea5486c5abe3</data>
